{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1461,"text":"So if I told you that\nthis was the face of pure joy,"},{"time":7177,"text":"would you call me crazy?"},{"time":10678,"text":"I wouldn't blame you,"},{"time":11918,"text":"because every time I look at this\nArctic selfie, I shiver just a little bit."},{"time":16920,"text":"I want to tell you\na little bit about this photograph."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19919,"text":"I was swimming around\nin the Lofoten Islands in Norway,"},{"time":23485,"text":"just inside the Arctic Circle,"},{"time":25190,"text":"and the water was hovering\nright at freezing."},{"time":28348,"text":"The air? A brisk -10 with windchill,"},{"time":32179,"text":"and I could literally feel the blood\ntrying to leave my hands,"},{"time":35615,"text":"feet and face, and rush\nto protect my vital organs."},{"time":40375,"text":"It was the coldest I've ever been."},{"time":43069,"text":"But even with swollen lips, sunken eyes,\nand cheeks flushed red,"},{"time":47921,"text":"I have found that this place right here\nis somewhere I can find great joy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54562,"text":"Now, when it comes to pain,\npsychologist Brock Bastian"},{"time":57627,"text":"probably said it best when he wrote,"},{"time":59972,"text":"\"Pain is a kind of shortcut\nto mindfulness."},{"time":62549,"text":"It makes us suddenly aware\nof everything in the environment."},{"time":66218,"text":"It brutally draws us in"},{"time":68192,"text":"to a virtual sensory awareness\nof the world much like meditation.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":73047,"text":"If shivering is a form of meditation,\nthen I would consider myself a monk."},{"time":76537,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":77387,"text":"Now, before we get into the why"},{"time":80266,"text":"would anyone ever want to surf\nin freezing cold water?"},{"time":83981,"text":"I would love to give you\na little perspective"},{"time":86558,"text":"on what a day in my life can look like."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89832,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":136017,"text":"(Video) Man: I mean, I know\nwe were hoping for good waves,"},{"time":139544,"text":"but I don't think anybody thought\nthat was going to happen."},{"time":142424,"text":"I can't stop shaking."},{"time":144095,"text":"I am so cold."}]},{"cues":[{"time":148344,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":151432,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156135,"text":"Chris Burkard: So,\nsurf photographer, right?"},{"time":159804,"text":"I don't even know\nif it's a real job title, to be honest."},{"time":162708,"text":"My parents definitely didn't think so"},{"time":164844,"text":"when I told them at 19 I was quitting\nmy job to pursue this dream career:"},{"time":169718,"text":"blue skies, warm tropical beaches,\nand a tan that lasts all year long."},{"time":174294,"text":"I mean, to me, this was it.\nLife could not get any better."},{"time":178125,"text":"Sweating it out, shooting surfers\nin these exotic tourist destinations."},{"time":182769,"text":"But there was just this one problem."},{"time":184510,"text":"You see, the more time I spent traveling\nto these exotic locations,"},{"time":188109,"text":"the less gratifying it seemed to be."},{"time":191104,"text":"I set out seeking adventure,\nand what I was finding was only routine."},{"time":195679,"text":"It was things like wi-fi, TV, fine dining,\nand a constant cellular connection"},{"time":200439,"text":"that to me were all the trappings\nof places heavily touristed"},{"time":203411,"text":"in and out of the water,"},{"time":205709,"text":"and it didn't take long\nfor me to start feeling suffocated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211106,"text":"I began craving wild, open spaces,"},{"time":215223,"text":"and so I set out to find the places\nothers had written off"},{"time":218665,"text":"as too cold, too remote,\nand too dangerous to surf,"},{"time":222543,"text":"and that challenge intrigued me."},{"time":225353,"text":"I began this sort of personal crusade\nagainst the mundane,"},{"time":229485,"text":"because if there's\none thing I've realized,"},{"time":232109,"text":"it's that any career,"},{"time":233961,"text":"even one as seemingly glamorous\nas surf photography,"},{"time":237722,"text":"has the danger of becoming monotonous."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240648,"text":"So in my search to break up\nthis monotony, I realized something:"},{"time":243702,"text":"There's only about a third\nof the Earth's oceans that are warm,"},{"time":246656,"text":"and it's really just that thin band\naround the equator."},{"time":249587,"text":"So if I was going to find perfect waves,"},{"time":252095,"text":"it was probably going\nto happen somewhere cold,"},{"time":254672,"text":"where the seas are notoriously rough,"},{"time":256553,"text":"and that's exactly where I began to look."},{"time":259246,"text":"And it was my first trip to Iceland"},{"time":261777,"text":"that I felt like I found\nexactly what I was looking for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":264846,"text":"I was blown away\nby the natural beauty of the landscape,"},{"time":268023,"text":"but most importantly, I couldn't believe\nwe were finding perfect waves"},{"time":272219,"text":"in such a remote and rugged\npart of the world."},{"time":275639,"text":"At one point, we got to the beach"},{"time":277915,"text":"only to find massive chunks of ice\nhad piled on the shoreline."},{"time":281018,"text":"They created this barrier\nbetween us and the surf,"},{"time":283371,"text":"and we had to weave \nthrough this thing like a maze"},{"time":285761,"text":"just to get out into the lineup."},{"time":287348,"text":"and once we got there,"},{"time":288473,"text":"we were pushing aside these ice chunks\ntrying to get into waves."},{"time":291511,"text":"It was an incredible experience,\none I'll never forget,"},{"time":295468,"text":"because amidst those harsh conditions,"},{"time":298254,"text":"I felt like I stumbled onto\none of the last quiet places,"},{"time":302976,"text":"somewhere that I found a clarity\nand a connection with the world"},{"time":305991,"text":"I knew I would never find\non a crowded beach."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310073,"text":"I was hooked. I was hooked. (Laughter)"},{"time":313231,"text":"Cold water was constantly on my mind,"},{"time":316087,"text":"and from that point on,"},{"time":317399,"text":"my career focused on these types of harsh\nand unforgiving environments,"},{"time":320729,"text":"and it took me to places like Russia,\nNorway, Alaska, Iceland, Chile,"},{"time":324605,"text":"the Faroe Islands,\nand a lot of places in between."},{"time":327534,"text":"And one of my favorite things\nabout these places"},{"time":330552,"text":"was simply the challenge and\nthe creativity it took just to get there:"},{"time":334453,"text":"hours, days, weeks spent on Google Earth"},{"time":336659,"text":"trying to pinpoint any remote stretch\nof beach or reef we could actually get to."},{"time":341418,"text":"And once we got there,\nthe vehicles were just as creative:"},{"time":344848,"text":"snowmobiles, six-wheel\nSoviet troop carriers,"},{"time":347757,"text":"and a couple of super-sketchy\nhelicopter flights."},{"time":351054,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":353260,"text":"Helicopters really scare me, by the way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":356510,"text":"There was this one particularly\nbumpy boat ride"},{"time":359042,"text":"up the coast of Vancouver Island\nto this kind of remote surf spot,"},{"time":362158,"text":"where we ended up watching\nhelplessly from the water"},{"time":364777,"text":"as bears ravaged our camp site."},{"time":367168,"text":"They walked off with our food\nand bits of our tent,"},{"time":370188,"text":"clearly letting us know that we\nwere at the bottom of the food chain"},{"time":373400,"text":"and that this was their spot, not ours."},{"time":375527,"text":"But to me, that trip"},{"time":377454,"text":"was a testament to the wildness\nI traded for those touristy beaches."}]},{"cues":[{"time":384066,"text":"Now, it wasn't until I traveled\nto Norway -- (Laughter) --"},{"time":388123,"text":"that I really learned\nto appreciate the cold."},{"time":392294,"text":"So this is the place"},{"time":394206,"text":"where some of the largest,\nthe most violent storms in the world"},{"time":397573,"text":"send huge waves smashing\ninto the coastline."},{"time":400627,"text":"We were in this tiny, remote fjord,\njust inside the Arctic Circle."},{"time":404605,"text":"It had a greater population\nof sheep than people,"},{"time":407151,"text":"so help if we needed it\nwas nowhere to be found."},{"time":410936,"text":"I was in the water \ntaking pictures of surfers,"},{"time":413151,"text":"and it started to snow."},{"time":416241,"text":"And then the temperature began to drop."},{"time":420458,"text":"And I told myself, there's not a chance\nyou're getting out of the water."},{"time":423843,"text":"You traveled all this way, and this is\nexactly what you've been waiting for:"},{"time":427437,"text":"freezing cold conditions\nwith perfect waves."},{"time":429519,"text":"And although I couldn't even feel\nmy finger to push the trigger,"},{"time":432537,"text":"I knew I wasn't getting out."},{"time":434049,"text":"So I just did whatever I could.\nI shook it off, whatever."},{"time":436842,"text":"But that was the point that I felt"},{"time":438525,"text":"this wind gush through\nthe valley and hit me,"},{"time":440644,"text":"and what started as this light snowfall\nquickly became a full-on blizzard,"},{"time":446058,"text":"and I started to lose\nperception of where I was."},{"time":450932,"text":"I didn't know if I was drifting\nout to sea or towards shore,"},{"time":454095,"text":"and all I could really make out\nwas the faint sound of seagulls"},{"time":458047,"text":"and crashing waves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":460810,"text":"Now, I knew this place had a reputation\nfor sinking ships and grounding planes,"},{"time":465646,"text":"and while I was out there floating,\nI started to get a little bit nervous."},{"time":470609,"text":"Actually, I was totally freaking out --"},{"time":472977,"text":"(Laughter) -- and I was\nborderline hypothermic,"},{"time":476414,"text":"and my friends eventually\nhad to help me out of the water."},{"time":479595,"text":"And I don't know if it was\ndelirium setting in or what,"},{"time":482752,"text":"but they told me later"},{"time":484912,"text":"I had a smile on my face the entire time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":490415,"text":"Now, it was this trip"},{"time":492528,"text":"and probably that exact experience\nwhere I really began to feel"},{"time":496312,"text":"like every photograph was precious,"},{"time":500272,"text":"because all of a sudden in that moment,\nit was something I was forced to earn."},{"time":505352,"text":"And I realized, all this shivering\nhad actually taught me something:"},{"time":510257,"text":"In life, there are no shortcuts to joy."},{"time":515120,"text":"Anything that is worth pursuing\nis going to require us to suffer"},{"time":518893,"text":"just a little bit,"},{"time":520855,"text":"and that tiny bit of suffering\nthat I did for my photography,"},{"time":524547,"text":"it added a value to my work\nthat was so much more meaningful to me"},{"time":527844,"text":"than just trying to fill\nthe pages of magazines."},{"time":531900,"text":"See, I gave a piece of myself\nin these places,"},{"time":538208,"text":"and what I walked away with"},{"time":540755,"text":"was a sense of fulfillment\nI had always been searching for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":546326,"text":"So I look back at this photograph."},{"time":549298,"text":"It's easy to see frozen fingers\nand cold wetsuits"},{"time":554018,"text":"and even the struggle\nthat it took just to get there,"},{"time":557082,"text":"but most of all,\nwhat I see is just joy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":561935,"text":"Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":563996,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}